---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us - Aloba Books">
  <Navigation />
  
  <main>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative py-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-500 via-teal-600 to-teal-700">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_center,rgba(255,255,255,0.1)_0%,transparent_70%)]"></div>
      <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6">About Us</h1>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- Content Section -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Welcome to Wright Books</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">For bookworms, by passionate writers</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
          <!-- Left Column - About Wright -->
          <div class="bg-teal-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="text-6xl font-bold text-teal-600 mr-6 leading-none">W</div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                  Wright Aloba has a master's degree in business administration from the College of William and Mary, Williamsburg, Virginia and a bachelor of accounting degree from Norfolk State University, Norfolk, Virginia. He was a former assistant professor of accounting and taxation for over 14 years.
                </p>
                <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                  He is currently in private practice as a Certified Public Accountant (CPA), specializing in taxation, accounting, financial and management consulting services. His passion, aside from his profession is education, in any form: Reading, learning and acquiring continuing knowledge everywhere available.
                </p>
                <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                  His weakness is very simple: He has no patience for complainers. He admires and attracted to people with positive + solution-oriented mindset.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Right Column - Vision -->
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">My Vision</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
              My vision is to let parents, guardians and leaders accept and internalize that part of loving all children everywhere is to show and guide them the right ways to function properly during their developmental stage in life. The right ways will include but are not limited to teaching them good character, hard work, respect for themselves, respect for others, how to plan for their future as if they're alone in this world (they may be alone someday), living a balanced life morally, physically, mentally and financially, so that in the end, they can leave this Mother Earth a better place than they arrived, for the future generations.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Mission Statement -->
        <div class="mt-16 text-center bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Our Mission</h3>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            To provide quality books, audiobooks, and educational content that inspire, educate, and empower readers of all ages. We believe in the transformative power of knowledge and strive to make learning accessible and enjoyable for everyone.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Values -->
        <div class="mt-16">
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center mb-12">Our Values</h3>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-teal-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-teal-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.746 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.246 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Education</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Committed to lifelong learning and knowledge sharing</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-teal-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-teal-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Passion</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Driven by love for books and storytelling</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-teal-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-teal-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Community</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Building connections through shared stories</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>

